HR NO. 211 ENROLLED
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
Legislature of Louisiana does hereby designate the month of May as Asthma and Allergy
Awareness Month in Louisiana and does hereby recognize the importance of raising
awareness for people with asthma and allergies in the state.
